Mikel Arteta on Reiss Nelson: &ldquo;I wouldn&rsquo;t like to compare [him with Sterling], what I will say is that Reiss has the potential to do whatever he wants. If he wants to do it, wants to learn &amp; wants to challenge himself, he can be a top, top player for this football club.&rdquo; #afc<br />
<br />
Arteta on Nelson: &ldquo;At the moment, I think he is on the right path with the right attitude &amp; then there are a lot of factors; he needs to deal with pressure, deliver every three days, score more goals &amp; make the difference more for the team because he has the quality to do that.&rdquo;

